{"tid":857804,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人返份工好大壓力","createTime":"2018-10-11T10:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T11:40:57.000Z","uid":44884,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"66aa04a18a0d9c38f418cdb3ef45871ca5724f4d","tid":857804,"uid":44884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T10:40:32.000Z","msg":"返既日子已經唔定 有時六日都要返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日驚比幾個老細屌 <br />\n有d case做完 到左放工甚至訓覺都係度諗會唔會做得唔好會比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時返去可以好hea 有時又忙到氣都喘唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n份工要對人兼又唔可以出錯 做得唔夠好又比個客投訴又比老細屌到飛天<br />\n唯一好就係人工算好糧又準 除此之外真係好攰好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無人份工都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738d877d5b19d92669089af858361540405bac2a","tid":857804,"uid":12096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:13:33.000Z","msg":"做做下就化架喇<br />\n唔會辛苦到一世ge<br />\n訓練放工唔好諗工事先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab491b5aeb1eecc6a00f0f0560764dcd7fb0bbf","tid":857804,"uid":55897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:52:05.000Z","msg":"成日驚唔唔夠時間做,返工做返,食LUNCH,食往來做,盡快放工前做唒,但都最段都唔得,因為臨放工又有野來,放工又諗往今日有冇野欠做,聽日又唔知工作量係點."},{"pid":"839df8604eb714455488038bd687b63bae8e2d95","tid":857804,"uid":44884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"738d877d5b19d92669089af858361540405bac2a","tid":857804,"uid":12096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:13:33.000Z","msg":"做做下就化架喇<br />\n唔會辛苦到一世ge<br />\n訓練放工唔好諗工事先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T12:28:45.000Z","msg":"控制唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86005c36f5975c314abe0e4f376569fdb3e4f44a","tid":857804,"uid":44884,"like":1,"